00:45:02,099 --> 00:45:03,340
To tell you the truth,

866
00:45:03,860 --> 00:45:05,300
actually, several times

867
00:45:05,700 --> 00:45:08,140
I have even written a letter of repudiation.

868
00:45:08,499 --> 00:45:09,740
But in the end,

869
00:45:10,340 --> 00:45:12,059
I burned them all.

870
00:45:14,140 --> 00:45:15,499
It's not for you,

871
00:45:16,780 --> 00:45:18,340
but for children's

872
00:45:18,340 --> 00:45:19,620
future marriage.

873
00:45:23,579 --> 00:45:25,700
As long as you understand a bit of reason,

874
00:45:25,979 --> 00:45:26,700
don't bring up divorce again

875
00:45:27,019 --> 00:45:29,660
in the future.
